Package engine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityLandscapeView
    A panel view to display the activation landscape view from the perspective of a specified agent, using colour to visualise the hill-climbing landscape and generated sub-goals.
    Engine
    A class to initialise a 2D grid-world River Crossing Dilemma environment and the agent population(s) that inhabit it.
    EnvironmentView
    A panel view to display the 2D environment from the overall perspective, using colour to indicate the different objects that exist in the environment.
    RealTimeGraph
    A class to generate a 2D line graph that can be used to visualise performance in real-time.
    View
    A class to display a visual representation of the environment, using an underlying model of the environment.
    ViewPanel
    A class to model the panel which displays a representation of the underlying model of the environment.
    WeightsParser
    A utility class to parse in weights from a file, and arrange them into an ArrayList containing 3D arrays of the weights that the file contains.
